name: Yoteslaya Wolf Head | Hoodie Pre-Order
description:
NOTE:Due to the high volume of orders, please allow 3-4 weeks for pre-orders to be printed & shipped after Nov 9th (All orders should be shipped by Dec 24th. Please contact if you haven't received an email notification regarding shipping AFTER the 24th. Thank you!) In memory of Yoteslaya, we decided to fulfil his last project he was working on with PredictableNOVA for his subscribers. The "Yoteslaya - Wolf Head" was designed by PredictableNOVA and is one of the many designs done for his projects collection. We will only be printing a minimum amount to start off with, if interested we highly suggest picking one up from the pre-orders. We hope to use any sales made to fund a memorial figurine design of a wolf character which PredictableNOVA created for Brian before his passing. This item will be available to his fans in memory of his gaming channel. Including a donation to his kids. DEADLINE FOR PRE-ORDERS IS NOV. 9TH, EST TIME --
  • 100% Cotton Jersey
  • Classic Fit
  • Soft hand print made in Canada (Montreal, QC)
  • Front Print w/ Wolf Head Logo & Signature
  • Sleeve Print w/ Name & Date
  • Designed by PredictableNOVA Free Shipping on all orders over $60 w/ code: MAILMAN
